title: LA Firefighters: "'No, We're All Getting on This Plane': How Matthew Stafford Helped Kelly To Come Out Of Her Guilt Trip" | NFL News - Times of India
text: It's no surprise that NFL WAGs often juggle family life, career, and supporting their husbands. But for Kelly Stafford, wife of LA Rams quarterback Matthew Stafford, the mental toll of balancing it all was real when she took her sick daughters to the Rams' wild-card game against the Minnesota Vikings. Kelly explained how she was overcome with guilt for taking her sick children to the game, and how Matthew helped her move forward.Guilty of Battling Family ResponsibilitiesDuring a recent episode of The Morning After podcast, Kelly shared the emotional struggles she faced leading up to the trip. With her daughters feeling under the weather, she wrestled with the guilt of whether it was right to be on a flight and at the game.There was a huge guilt factor,\" Kelly said, reflecting on the flight. \"I was thinking, 'Should we even be on this plane right now with everyone surrounding us and all the players preparing for the game?' But Matthew said, 'Get your ass on that plane. We all need to be together'\" Her husband's reassuring words lifted her spirits, reminding her that sometimes family needs to stick together, no matter the circumstances.https://youtu.be/W3eT7gaTWnU?si=GYEg1vs9FLda1L86The Support of Matthew StaffordIt was Matthewâ€™s mental support that helped Kelly feel confident in her decision to attend the game. Despite her doubts, Matthewâ€™s insistence on their unity helped push past her guilt.Kelly recalled, \"That was such an incredible thing for me to hear because there was a little bit of like, â€˜Should I just stay back with my children?â€™ Matthew was like, â€™No, we will do whatever it takes. We are all getting on this plane. We are going to be together right now.\" The fact that Matt had been steady, as they all were going to get through this together.Acknowledging The LA HeroesAs for Kelly, she had sleep disorders because of the fires; however, what triggered her is when she got concerned about whether the fires are coming closer or the city she resides in, as it created fear in her that kept her from sleeping well, adding up her stress level.Her emotional messages about the LA firefighters and their sacrifices remind us to recognize the unsung heroes working behind the scenes.\"I just pray for the safety of these individuals and for God to come in the hearts of their families and protect them. We don't thank our First Responders enough ever. You know it always takes something like this for everyone to go to the firehouses and to thank them but really we should be doing that all the time.\"Kelly Stafford's journey through guilt, family struggles, and supporting her husband while battling personal demons shows the strength in her. She was able to push through because of Matthew and the importance of family, even when the obstacles were too overwhelming.Also read - Trolling Hits Hard for NFL WAGs, and Girlfriend of Braxton Berrios Alix Earle Is No Exceptionâ€”Hereâ€™s How It Affected Her and How She Developed Thick Skin Amid Online Criticism

author: Trinity Archie
title: The Hidden Downsides To Cleaning Plastic Toilet Seats With Soft Scrub
text:
Removing bacteria and grime from a toilet seat is a rather simple task, but it can be surprisingly destructive when the wrong cleaning product is used. This is especially true for plastic toilet seats that are often less durable than other materials. Soft Scrub is among the cleaning products you should avoid using on plastic toilet seats. The abrasive calcium carbonate included in the formula may scratch this material, leaving you with an unsightly toilet seat that would need to be repaired.
Advertisement Although the calcium carbonate pieces in Soft Scrub make the perfect exfoliator for scrubbing dirt and grime away from surfaces that are a bit more scratch-resistant, you should be cautious about using the product on a plastic toilet seat. Some customers have even shared first-hand experience of the damage caused by this product. It is best to save your Soft Scrub for surfaces that can handle its scrubbing power and turn to more gentle products, which is one of many tips on how to clean your toilet .
Soft Scrub can scratch plastic toilet seats @anxietyscrubs I sprayed my toilet brush with Clorox bleach spray last night and let it dry cause thatâ€™s what I see all yâ€™all doing and I woke up to the brush being orange ðŸ˜­ðŸ˜­ðŸ˜­ why does this happen to me ðŸ’€ #cleantok #moptok #ReTokforNature #cleaningmotivation #laundrytok #amazonfinds #targetfinds #mustbuy #cleaningtips #cleaninghacks #squeakyclean #cleanwithme #transformation #asmrsounds
â™¬ Hold Me Closer - Elton John & Britney Spears
If you have been tempted to try any plastic toilet seat cleaning hacks that involve the use of Soft Scrub, the TikTok posted by user @anxietyscrubs might just convince you that this is not the wisest decision. As you can see in the video above, the content creator explained that the product scratched a plastic toilet seat in a previous apartment. Additionally, @anxietyscrubs warned against using steel wool pads on this surface. With this in mind, you may also want to avoid cleaning plastic toilet seats with harsh scrubbing brushes, scouring pads, or any other tools or solutions that are super abrasive.
Advertisement It is important to note that the Soft Scrub website confirms the product can be used in a toilet bowl, but does not state that it can be safely used on a plastic toilet seat. This may explain why @anxietyscrubs accidentally damaged the surface with this product. While using Soft Scrub on a plastic toilet seat is a risk, there's no problem using it inside your toilet bowl. The cleaning solution can clean more durable surfaces without causing scratches thanks to the low hardness rating of calcium carbonate. This scrubbing ingredient is rated at level 3 on the Moh's Hardness Scale.
How to clean a plastic toilet seat safely
Eggeeggjiew/Getty Images
There is no special toilet cleaning trick you need to rely on to remove grime from a plastic toilet seat. The process is super simple. To clean this surface, start out by applying a mild, non-abrasive cleaning solution or a neutral soap all over. You can make the soap easier to apply by pouring it into a spray bottle and thinning it out with water. Spray the entire seat with the solution. Next, use a gentle cleaning cloth, paper towel, or sponge to wipe the cleaning solution away. It should have loosened up any grime to make it easier to remove. You may need to repeat this process to tackle particularly stubborn stains. Feel free to let the cleaning solution sit for a few minutes to allow it to really penetrate any grime that refuses to budge.
Advertisement You can use this same cleaning solution to tackle your toilet's hinges and lid. Simply spray it onto these surfaces and wipe it away with a cloth or sponge. Do not forget that you can go in with Soft Scrub or your favorite toilet bowl cleaning solution when tackling your toilet bowl if needed. This may help you remove built up grime easier than a simple soap and water solution.

author: Bar Mor Hazut
title: 'I'm not on duty, back off': Doctor refuses to provide medical care on flight, passenger tries forcing him to do so anyway - FAIL Blog - Funny Fails
text: What type of passenger are you on a long flight? Are you the type who falls asleep as soon as the plane takes off, only waking up when the meal is being served and when the plane lands? Or are you the type that never falls asleep, so you binge-watch an entire TV show while snacking on the complimentary snacks and drinks, and maybe chat a bit with your neighboring passenger? I think it's great that every person can find what to do on a flight in order to relax and enjoy the experience, but the experience for doctors on flights can become something entirely different. It is no secret that doctors have a greater responsibility than most of the other professions, but you would think that on their time off, they would be able to relax and let loose a bit. Apparently not, as in this Reddit story, a doctor shares that while on a flight, he decided to give himself a break and enjoy a few drinks. He chatted for a while with the woman sitting next to him, telling her he was a doctor, when an announcement was made asking for a doctor to assist a passenger on the plane. Since he already had several drinks he wasn't feeling up to the task, but the passenger next to him was extremely mad about his decision to sit this one out. Scroll down for the full tale, and for the surprising comments who were not all in favor of the doctor. title: ZABâ€™s birth anniversary celebrated
text: LAHORE:The 96th birth anniversary of Pakistan People's Party's founder Zulfikar Ali Bhutto was celebrated here on Sunday at Bangash House, the residence of former PPP MPA Dr Zia Ullah Khan Bangash. PPP candidates from NA-118 Mian Shahid Abbas, from PP-148, Khawaja Abdul Rehman, former member of District Lahore Assembly Attia Salim, Nasreen Gilani, Mian Zahid, Shahid Sulehri and large number of jialas attended the event. Speaking on the occasion, member Federal Council and former MPA of PPP Dr Zia Ullah Khan Bangash said party was united under the leadership of Chairman Bilawal Bhutto Zardari.
